    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69182.0,
      "end_time": 72582.0,
      "text": "All the time travel in the world can't make someone love you."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 72582.0,
      "end_time": 77494.0,
      "text": "「不管再怎麼樣的穿越時空，也無法使一個不愛你的人愛上你。」"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77494.0,
      "end_time": 82237.0,
      "text": "Tim kept going back in time，trying to let his first love，Charlotte，fall in love with him"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82237.0,
      "end_time": 84562.0,
      "text": "but he ended up failing"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84562.0,
