    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 102933.0,
      "end_time": 105652.0,
      "text": "What do you have to do as Little Drops do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 105652.0,
      "end_time": 108753.0,
      "text": "make all your friends watch this video!!"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 124143.0,
      "end_time": 129133.0,
      "text": "The real troubles in your life will always be things that never crossed your worried mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 129133.00000000001,
      "end_time": 134784.0,
      "text": "「人生當中發生的真正災禍，往往都是那些，你從沒設想過的事。」"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 134784.0,
      "end_time": 138434.0,
      "text": "When people live，they keep worrying about different things"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 138434.0,
      "end_time": 141534.0,
      "text": "The worry may be as small as a test to as big as the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 141534.0,
      "end_time": 143944.0,
      "text": "so the worried mind is a description"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 143944.0,
      "end_time": 147877.0,
      "text": "Cross one’s mind means 經過某人的想法"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 147877.0,
      "end_time": 150750.0,
      "text": "so it means you thought about something"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 150750.0,
      "end_time": 154863.0,
      "text": "Has it ever crossed your mind that Crown spent hours working on this video?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 154863.0,
      "end_time": 157574.0,
      "text": "So make all your friends watch this video!!"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 165304.0,
      "end_time": 168674.0,
      "text": "Life's a mixed bag, no matter who you are."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 168674.0,
      "end_time": 172420.0,
      "text": "「不管你是誰，人生就是會經歷各種酸甜苦辣。」"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 172420.0,
      "end_time": 177894.0,
      "text": "Tim's father always give him directions and wisdom."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 177894.0,
      "end_time": 181152.0,
      "text": "He said that despite being able to travel in time，it doesn't guarantee a wonderful life"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 181152.0,
      "end_time": 184434.0,
      "text": "a mixed bag is a container holding all kinds of things"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 184434.0,
      "end_time": 188220.0,
      "text": "so sometime life is beautiful but sometimes it is hard"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 188220.0,
      "end_time": 190768.0,
      "text": "when mixed is used as verb，it means 混合"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 190768.0,
      "end_time": 195994.0,
      "text": "If you add -ed，it becomes an adj，which means with all kinds of situations"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 195994.0,
      "end_time": 198866.0,
      "text": "It's like what Forrest Gump said"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 198866.0,
      "end_time": 202076.0,
      "text": "Life is like a box of chocolate, you never know what you’re gonna get"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 202076.0,
      "end_time": 203274.0,
      "text": "they have similar meaning"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 218304.0,
      "end_time": 222575.0,
      "text": "Try and marry someone kind. And this is a kind man with a good heart."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 222575.0,
      "end_time": 228464.0,
      "text": "「試著找一位善良的伴侶。而這一位就是一個好心腸的善良男人。」"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 228464.0,
      "end_time": 232418.0,
      "text": "In the movie，the conversation between Tom and his dad is always really touching"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 232418.0,
      "end_time": 234745.0,
      "text": "and warm as well"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 234745.0,
      "end_time": 237525.0,
      "text": "We can see the love for his son"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 237525.0,
      "end_time": 241738.0,
      "text": "and his philosophy clearly"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 241738.0,
      "end_time": 244925.0,
      "text": "this is a simple one，so not much talk about"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 244925.0,
      "end_time": 247835.0,
      "text": "but we can connect kind and heart"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 247835.0,
      "end_time": 251535.0,
      "text": "it'll become an adjective，kindhearted"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 269175.0,
      "end_time": 274463.0,
      "text": "I just try to live every day as if I've deliberately come back to this one day to enjoy it"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 274463.0,
      "end_time": 279596.0,
      "text": "as if it was the full final day of my extraordinary ordinary life."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 279596.0,
      "end_time": 285495.0,
      "text": "「我試著每天都如同已經特地穿越時空又回到同樣的這一天來生活著」"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 285495.0,
      "end_time": 290655.0,
      "text": "「把這天當作是我非凡的平凡人生中的最後一天來享受著」"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 290655.0,
      "end_time": 294505.0,
      "text": "Tim listened to his father's suggestion and carried it out in a higher level"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 294505.0,
      "end_time": 299296.0,
      "text": "which is to live everyday as if he has deliberately come back to this one day to enjoy it"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 299296.0,
      "end_time": 302726.0,
      "text": "Deliberately is a hard one，but it isn't uncommon"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 302726.0,
      "end_time": 305041.0,
      "text": "it means 刻意的，故意的"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 305041.0,
      "end_time": 308326.0,
      "text": "synonyms are intentionally and purposely"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 308326.0,
      "end_time": 311606.0,
      "text": "As if it was is a subjunctive mood"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 311606.0,
      "end_time": 315205.0,
      "text": "in Chinese it means 如同什麼什麼一樣"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 315205.0,
      "end_time": 318517.0,
      "text": "we all know that ordinary stands for 一般"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 318517.0,
      "end_time": 320715.0,
      "text": "if you add extra"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 320715.0,
      "end_time": 323760.0,
      "text": "it means its not in the ordinary zone"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 323760.0,
      "end_time": 327325.0,
      "text": "so extraordinary means 非凡、特別"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 327325.0,
      "end_time": 332397.0,
      "text": "putting extraordinary ordinary kinda has a rhyme"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 332397.0,
      "end_time": 334706.0,
      "text": "reminding me of pen pineapple apple pen"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 350606.0,
      "end_time": 354106.0,
      "text": "We're all travelling through time together every day of our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 354106.0,
      "end_time": 358190.0,
      "text": "All we can do is do our best to relish this remarkable ride."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 358190.0,
      "end_time": 361466.0,
      "text": "「我們其實每一天都一起穿梭在時空當中。」"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 361466.0,
      "end_time": 366236.0,
      "text": "「我們能做的就是盡其所能的珍惜這美妙的人生旅程。」"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 366236.0,
      "end_time": 369736.0,
      "text": "I like the quote's concept of space traveling"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 369736.0,
      "end_time": 373746.0,
