      "text": "but we are living through time"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 378718.0,
      "end_time": 381878.0,
      "text": "Relish is a rare，but beautiful word"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 381878.0,
      "end_time": 384297.0,
      "text": "it's meaning is 享受、喜愛"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 384297.0,
      "end_time": 387346.0,
      "text": "Remarkable is remark plus able"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 387346.0,
      "end_time": 391076.0,
      "text": "remark means 評論，and able is 有能力"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 391076.0,
      "end_time": 393947.0,
      "text": "So if something is worth commenting"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 393947.0,
      "end_time": 396067.0,
      "text": "it means it's something nice"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 396067.0,
      "end_time": 398287.0,
      "text": "and worth spending time on"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 398287.0,
      "end_time": 402503.0,
      "text": "and there is actually a poem technique here，called alliteration"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 402503.0,
      "end_time": 407498.0,
